ActConstitution Act, 1867
SubjectAdministrator of the Government of Ontario
PrecisOrder replacing paragraphs (h) and (i) of P.C. 2013-1059 of October 7, 2013 to appoint the Hon. HEATHER J. SMITH to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of ONTARIO from October 30 to 31, 2013, inclusive, instead of the Hon. WARREN K. WINKLER.
